    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly pristine, showroom-quality condition. Every aspect of the car has been meticulously maintained, from the flawless exterior paint to the immaculate interior upholstery. Mechanically, it operates perfectly with no signs of wear, providing a driving experience that feels as if the car just rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle in absolute mint condition with a complete service history.",
