      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine. This unit delivers a visceral driving experience via its 6-speed manual transaxle and rear-wheel-drive configuration. The VarioCam Plus system provides seamless power delivery, while the chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity. This example has been proactively maintained with an IMS bearing retrofit and a recent cooling system overhaul. While the aesthetic reflects honest road use, the drivetrain remains tight with no signs of bore scoring or oil aeration. A driver-focused machine for the purist seeking analog feedback and precision engineering.",
